{"tid":2450220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"據報福士汽車將裁員五千人","createTime":"2021-03-17T08:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T10:19:34.000Z","uid":295230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"af80392157ebf92b5c6fd46d15d83363af716abc","tid":2450220,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"德國《商報》(Handelsblatt)報道，福士汽車計劃通過向較年長僱員提供提早退休方案，以裁員最多5,000人，預計涉資5億歐元，但長遠將可節省數十億歐元。<br />\n<br />\n福士汽車發言人表示，集團已經與工會商定計劃，將向1964年出生的員工提部供部分退休計劃，同時亦會為年齡較大的員工提供提前退休計劃。<br />\n<br />\n報道又提到，福士汽車將凍結招聘直至今年底，而聘請外部員工只會在資訊科技及軟件等"},{"pid":"d1e287e2bea7a664973155c0a35b5eecba5a05d5","tid":2450220,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1082555/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1082555%2F2&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=00678501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1082555/2</a>"},{"pid":"bc9337acb4b4e5a7ab64c7637eef4113c336b0e8","tid":2450220,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:19:34.000Z","msg":"幾時再short squeeze<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}